data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER     Lovely 1 Story 4 bedroom 2 bath home offering a open floor plan to the  Family Room and Dining Room which opens up to the Kitchen with a Breakfast Area. Also includes a large Covered Patio with ceiling fan,  inside Utility Room, a Spacious Primary Bedroom 16 x 20 with a Large Walk-in Closet.   This home is 3 years old, full yard  sprinklers, gutters on the home, tankless water heater in garage, window blinds and All appliances stay with home.  Home features Vinyl plank flooring through out the living area and hallway.  The kitchen has - 36" Flat Panel Maple- Espresso cabinets, granite counters. Home is  located close to shopping area, movies and Restaurants  in Nearby Valley Ranch Town Center. A Must see  home for your family
